arrangement.p:
The Order of the Spoon Records are arranged in 6 series: I. Articles of Organization and
				Membership, 1930-1939; II. Meeting Notices, 1928-1939; III. Programs for Ceremonies, 1936-1937;
				IV. Correspondence, 1934-1938; V. Financial Reports, 1935-1938; and VI. Artifacts, circa 1935.
